PHP Password Manager (ppma) Change Log
======================================

Version 0.3.4
-------------
- New: Added widget to sidebar that shows the most viewed entries

Version 0.3.3
-------------
- New: Added widget to sidebar that shows the recent entries
- Chg: Removed unused files
